show.title: Waking Up As The Richest

show.sharing_text_v2:
हेलो! मैंने कुकू एफएम पर इस शो को सुना और मेरे ख्‍याल से आपको भी पसंद आएगा 
https://links.kukufm.com/Qu8G3v
show.description: Once betrayed and left for dead, Arjun rises from the shadows with only one mission—revenge. With every step, he unravels the empire of his former ally Devraj, the man who stole everything. Waking Up As The Richest  is a gripping tale of justice, betrayal, and the unstoppable wrath of a fallen warrior.
